<%= render :layout => 'layouts/groups_layout' do%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">
    <title>Carousel Template for Bootstrap</title>
    <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="../../assets/js/html5shiv.js"></script>
      <script src="../../assets/js/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
    <!-- Custom styles for this template -->
    <style>
    /*FUTURETTES DIVIDE*/
    .featurette-divider {
        margin: 80px 0; /* Space out the Bootstrap <hr> more */
      }
      .featurette {
        padding-top: 120px; /* Vertically center images part 1: add padding above and below text. */
        overflow: hidden; /* Vertically center images part 2: clear their floats. */
      }
      .featurette-image {
        margin-top: -120px; /* Vertically center images part 3: negative margin up the image the same amount of the padding to center it. */
      }
      /* Give some space on the sides of the floated elements so text doesn't run right into it. */
      .featurette-image.pull-left {
        margin-right: 40px;
      }
      .featurette-image.pull-right {
        margin-left: 40px;
      }
      /* Thin out the marketing headings */
      .featurette-heading {
        font-size: 50px;
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
    <!-- Carousel
    ================================================== -->
    <div class=row>
      <div class="hidden-sm col-md-1 col-lg-1">
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-10 col-lg-9">
        <div id="carousel-example-generic" class="carousel slide">
          <!-- Indicators -->
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>
          <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="item active">
              <img src="/assets/docentes.jpg" alt="...">
              <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                  <h1>Comunidad abierta</h1>
                  <p>Adquiere y comparte conocimiento</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item pull-center">
              <img src="/assets/docentes1.jpg" alt="...">
              <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                  <h1>Ingresa ahora</h1>
                  <p>Ingresa ahora a nuestro sistema y aprovecha las oportunidades que te brinda</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item pull-center">
              <img src="/assets/estudiantes.jpg" alt="...">
              <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                  <h1>Comparte conocimiento</h1>
                  <p>Conocimiento a montones y de manera gratuita</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
            <!-- Controls -->
            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="icon-prev"></span>
            </a>
            <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="next">
            </a>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /.carousel -->
    </div>
  </div>
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <br>
    <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->
    <div class="container marketing">
      <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
      <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->
      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="featurette">
        <img class="featurette-image pull-right" src="http://placehold.it/500x500">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Foro abierto <span class="muted">Locura total</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Compartir conocimiento, ahora es facilango. Aporta y pregunta, asi funciona todo.</p>
      </div>
      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="featurette">
        <img class="featurette-image pull-left" src="http://placehold.it/500x500">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Ahora es mas facil <span class="muted">Velo tu mismo.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Con nuestro acceso directo a los temas dentro del foro, comentar y aportar conocimiento nunca fue mas sencillo</p>
      </div>
      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="featurette" style="margin-bottom:40px;">
        <img class="featurette-image pull-right" src="/assets/flaco.jpg">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Busqueda de contenido <span class="muted"> Chekealo.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Nuestro buscador de contenido ayudara a encontrar aquello que andas buscando, con una facilidad increible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
          <img class="img-circle" src="http://placehold.it/140x140" alt="Generic placeholder image">
          <h2>Docente</h2>
          <p>Con tu colaboracion podremos brindar y compartir conocimiento tanto abierto como privado. Compartir tus experiencias nos servira a todos</p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
          <img class="img-circle" src="http://placehold.it/140x140" alt="Generic placeholder image">
          <h2>Estudiante</h2>
          <p>Es complicado caminar solo; pero cuando caminas en grupo es mucho mejor. Adquirir y aportar conocimiento es una parte fundamental del aprendizaje.</p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
          <img class="img-circle" src="http://placehold.it/140x140"  alt="Generic placeholder image">
          <h2>Profesional</h2>
          <p>Tu experiencia laboral es de gran aporte para nosotros. Nunca se deja de aprender y no esta de más enseñar.</p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
      </div><!-- /.row -->
      <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->
    </div>
    <!-- Bootstrap core JavaScript
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->
    <!--<script src="../../assets/js/jquery.js"></script>
    <script src="../../dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../assets/js/holder.js"></script>-->
  </body>
</html>
<%end%>
